Set 2

* - 2nd Verse Only

reviews.review_text: crowd enters under cut fence This was a very quickly sold-out show. I was there that evening and traveled from I.U.P where I was attending college at the time. My roommate took a pair of bolt cutters and cut the fence, so needless to say, there were a whole lot of very grateful fans without a miracle that received one.  Funny shit, the roommate got caught by security, cuffed, and sent out of the back of amphitheatre and back into the lot. It was a wonderful show!!!!

Just okay show but terrible ‘fans’ The vibe here was pretty tension-filled. There were hundreds and hundreds of fans in the lot that didn’t have tickets, which is usually okay, of course.  But they seemed extra restless.  And then some serious a-holes used bolt cutters to cut the fence and get into the show. It is this kind of stuff that changed the scene too much for me.
